high_descs: Turn around and walk straight to face the end of the black table with the brown lamp on it.
Pick up the pencil from off of the black table.
Turn around, go straight, then go right and stop to face the black table on the left.
Place the pencil in the silver bowl on the black table.
Pick up the silver bowl that's on the table.
Go to the left, then right, then right at the couch and face the end of the glass coffee table.
Place the silver bowl on the glass coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place the silver bowl with the pencil in it on the glass coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the small rectangular table with the lamp.
Pick up the pencil on the table.
Turn around and walk ahead and veer right at the wall to the rectangular table.
Place the pencil in the bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl.
Turn right and walk ahead and around the couch to the coffee table.
Place the bowl on the coffee table to the right of the other object.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a pencil in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the small black table with the lamp on it to the right of the couch.
Pick up the yellow pencil off of the small black table.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the small black table below the picture on the wall.
Put the pencil in the bowl that is on the black table.
Pick up the bowl with the pencil in it off of the table.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the bowl with the pencil in it on top of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a pencil in it on the coffee table.
